      "writtenOn": "2021-03-31T03:59:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think you need to call Flatten on this (https://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/04cc9a23bff6/common/errors/multierror.go#98) to squeeze out the nils.\n\nnote:\n\n  var err error\n  err \u003d errors.MultiError{nil, nil}\n  if err !\u003d nil {\n    panic(err) // this will panic\n  }\n\n  if errors.Flatten(err) !\u003d nil {\n    panic(err) // this will not\n  }\n\nAlternately you could use LazyMultiError which has this \u0027flatten\u0027 functionality built in.",
      "revId": "b3e04cff53ae54825b1628a9371bb3217d4155e0",
